## Projects
+ [Fuel Efficiency](https://github.com/stats295r-fa20/hw1-ewongtoi)
  + Analysis on a small data set comparing the fuel efficiency of SP98 and
    E10fuel.

+ [Coronavirus Reproduction Number](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1O03W0aG2CuLJuj4XOGX90MJlvaU522Bz/view?usp=sharing)
  + Class project with Isaac Goldstein estimating the reproduction number for
    coronavirus in Hubei province fit to data from early 2020. We applied the
    technique of linear noise approximation to data from early 2020 and fit a
    susceptible-infectious-recovered (SIR) model.
